      "comment": "ABDULLA ZULU (2) was below best last time when sixth at Sandown but three back was a Special conditions race winner in the quickest time on the card at Sandown. Has the ability and can find winning form this time. LAKEVIEW LYNETTE (3) goes very well this trip starting 10 times for six wins and three minors. Was out of placings last time (35.28) at The Meadows in a Grade 4/5, finishing sixth and beaten 8 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. HEY PRESTO (1) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from four tries. Placed last time (26.02) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing second and beaten 3 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. PAW ZENITH (5) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.",
